TITLE: China reports 60,000 coronavirus-related deaths from December after concerns of underreporting
SUMMARY: Beijing finally reported nearly 60,000 coronavirus deaths since Dec. 8 and after reporting nearly none since a surge hit in October and after it lifted lockdown restrictions.

TITLE: UK commits to sending Ukraine Challenger 2 tanks, going further than Biden admin
SUMMARY: The United Kingdom pledged to send Ukraine Challenger 2 tanks Saturday as its forces engage in a brutal warfare on the eastern front.

TITLE: Dozens trapped and injured after Russia struck 9-story apartment building in Ukraine's Dnipro
SUMMARY: Kyiv was hit Saturday with missile strikes in the first attack since the New Year kicked off two weeks ago, though no causalities have been reported.

TITLE: Border crisis: 3 girls abandoned near Rio Grande, Mexican officials make rescue
SUMMARY: Mexican National Guard officials successfully rescued Wednesday three young siblings that were left to fend for themselves near the US-Mexico border.

TITLE: UK schools ban physical contact, prevent students from holding hands, hugging
SUMMARY: Two schools in England have issued guidelines banning students from making physical contact on-site to ensure the safety of their students. Parents received the change positively.

TITLE: Ali Reza Akbari: Iran executes former senior defense official over British spy claims
SUMMARY: Iran executed Ali Reza Akbari, the country's former defense ministry official, by hanging after convicting him of being a spy for Britain's MI-6 intelligence agency without evidence.

TITLE: ROTTING IN DUBAI: Family of American imprisoned in UAE says US abandoned him for Brittney Griner
SUMMARY: Zack Shahin, an American who has been rotting in a Dubai prison for 15 years was "abandoned" by the U.S., his family says as they plead for mercy before his death.

TITLE: War game suggests U.S. needs to bolster Taiwan's defenses now to avoid heavy casualties
SUMMARY: The Center for Strategic & International Studies conducted war games mimicking a 2026 Chinese invasion of Taiwan. The scenarios found the U.S. has to do more to prepare in case of a potential invasion.

TITLE: Debate in Spain over regional abortion rights restrictions
SUMMARY: Spain debated regional abortion rights and restrictions, as new measures in Castile and Leon angered abortion activists.

TITLE: Mass. student dead after fall from Cancun Airbnb balcony; boyfriend arrested, cleared of wrongdoing: reports
SUMMARY: A 20-year-old Massachusetts woman is dead after falling from the balcony of an Airbnb while vacationing in Cancun, Mexico, with her boyfriend, who was arrested but released.
